# CMake (generated only — build*/ above already covers the generated
# top-level Makefile CMake emits in a build dir; a bare "Makefile" rule here
# would also match hand-written source Makefiles like mcu/*/Makefile, which
# are real, tracked files, not build output)
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
